cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.DB 

The paper focuses on machine learning and automation in defining predictive tasks for event-driven time-series data. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves interaction with data scientists, which could fall under social and information networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper deals with data management and organization, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and databases (cs.DB).
